description: This file defines a reasoning agent that uses OpenAI's GPT-4 model to analyze historical factors related to the Treaty of Versailles, including political, economic, and social impacts, and their influence on the onset of World War II.

classes.name: Agent
classes.description: A class representing an AI agent capable of performing reasoning tasks.
